---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service">
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-canvas-night text-on-primary min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold mb-12 uppercase tracking-tight">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-12 font-body text-mute leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-primary uppercase mb-4 tracking-wider">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing and using the Skardu Essence website (skarduessence.com), you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-primary uppercase mb-4 tracking-wider">2. Product Information & Purity</h2>
          <p>
            We strive to provide accurate descriptions of our Himalayan products. However, as our products are natural and wild-crafted (such as Shilajit, Honey, and Saffron), variations in color, texture, and consistency may occur. These are signs of authenticity and do not constitute product defects.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-primary uppercase mb-4 tracking-wider">3. WhatsApp Ordering Process</h2>
          <p>
            Skardu Essence utilizes a manual checkout process via WhatsApp. By clicking "Proceed to Checkout," you will be redirected to our official WhatsApp business account. 
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li>An order request via WhatsApp does not constitute a final sale until confirmed by our team.</li>
            <li>Payment details and shipping arrangements will be finalized during the WhatsApp conversation.</li>
            <li>We reserve the right to refuse any order request.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-primary uppercase mb-4 tracking-wider">4. Pricing & Payment</h2>
          <p>
            All prices are listed in Pakistani Rupees (PKR). We reserve the right to change prices at any time without notice. Since we do not process payments directly on our website, you are responsible for ensuring the security of your payment through the methods agreed upon via WhatsApp.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-primary uppercase mb-4 tracking-wider">5. Shipping & Delivery</h2>
          <p>
            Delivery times may vary based on your location and the seasonal availability of certain products. We are not responsible for delays caused by logistics providers or regional constraints in Gilgit-Baltistan.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-primary uppercase mb-4 tracking-wider">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on this site, including but not limited to the "Skardu Essence" name, logos, product descriptions, and original photography, is the property of Skardu Essence and is protected by copyright laws.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-primary uppercase mb-4 tracking-wider">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            Skardu Essence shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting from the use or inability to use our products or website.
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="pt-12 border-t border-hairline-on-dark text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">
          <p>Last Updated: June 2026</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Skardu, Gilgit-Baltistan, Pakistan</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
